text: Nice place for lunch and dinner. My first time visiting. They sell deserts too. Had nice chendol!! Yummy. Tried the western stall. Their chicken chop is nice. I later went back to tabao satays, stingrays and sotong for dinner. All very nice especially the stingray very well prepared!!!
The western food is nice and the portion is just right. Worth your money. Place is clean but hot

Nice and clean place but remember to bring your own containers as they charges for plastic use. New zhizhar stall and mala fried rice at reasonable price. New Mookata stall but Western stall got new tenant.

2nd time here for the Western food from Kaki Corner. Its so affordable with big portion. I had Blackpepper Chicken Chop with rice and tasted so good, there was fries and coleslaw too.
The coffeeshop is clean and brightly lit, but can be a little inaccessible if you dont have a vehicle. Nearest mrt will be pioneer mrt.
Its open on weekends too.
nice food , affordable price. spacious seating area
